data.description: Welcome to your spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom sanctuary in Silver Springs, Florida, nestled on an expansive 1.10-acre lot with A1 zoning. This property offers not only the serenity of acreage but also versatile options for all your financing needs. Furthermore, rest easy knowing that an engineer's report is readily available, ensuring confidence in your purchase. As you step inside, you'll be delighted to find a bonus room/flex room, perfect for customization to suit your lifestyle. Additionally, a convenient shed on the property provides ample storage space for your convenience. Boasting just under 2,000 square feet of living space, this residence offers room to spread out and thrive. Each of the bedrooms features walk-in closets, providing generous storage solutions. The primary bathroom is a retreat in itself, featuring a soaking tub and a separate shower. Natural light abounds, courtesy of skylights scattered throughout the open floor plan, creating an inviting and bright ambiance. This property is more than just a home; it's an opportunity to embrace the Florida lifestyle. Don't miss out on the chance to make it your own!
